rows.label: qst640203_msg0001
rows.name:
Welcome back, Idaten! How
did it go this time?

rows.label: qst640203_msg0002
rows.name:
Everything went perfectly, and
I didn't eat a single thing!

rows.label: qst640203_msg0004
rows.name:
And Ciamran was really happy to get
his delivery. It's all thanks to
you and your hard work, Idaten.

rows.label: qst640203_msg0005
rows.name:
If you don't mind, do you think
you could keep up this delivery
job, Idaten? It'd be a great help.

rows.label: qst640203_msg0006
rows.name:
Totally! And I know I can
resist the temptation to
eat what I'm carrying!

rows.label: qst640203_msg0007
rows.name:
The customers have such happy faces
when I make the deliveries! It makes
me all warm and fuzzy inside...

rows.label: qst640203_msg0008
rows.name:
Also, I realized it's better to arrive
with an empty stomach, ready for whatever
local delicacies I can gobble!

rows.label: qst640203_msg0009
rows.name:
I...suppose that's one
way to look at it.

rows.label: qst640203_msg0010
rows.name:
Well, you'll be glad to know
I've still got loads of
requests from all over Alst.

rows.label: qst640203_msg0011
rows.name:
I'll let you know what needs doing,
so if you have a bit of time to
help out, I'd be super grateful.

rows.label: qst640203_msg0013
rows.name:
In the name of good food,
I feel I can do anything!
Including deliveries.

rows.label: qst640203_msg0016
rows.name:
I wanted to say thank you. Because
of you, all kinds of people have had
the chance to sample my desserts.

rows.label: qst640203_msg0017
rows.name:
Well, it's not like supporting
Just Desserts is my job or
anything! But you're very welcome.
